		<title>真狗假狗分不清！男子雕刻愛犬木像 網讚：超逼真 </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/04/%e7%9c%9f%e7%8b%97%e5%81%87%e7%8b%97%e5%88%86%e4%b8%8d%e6%b8%85%ef%bc%81%e7%94%b7%e5%ad%90%e9%9b%95%e5%88%bb%e6%84%9b%e7%8a%ac%e6%9c%a8%e5%83%8f-%e7%b6%b2%e8%ae%9a%ef%bc%9a%e8%b6%85%e9%80%bc%e7%9c%9f/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 洪瑜蓉]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 04 Sep 2025 06:28:02 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[時事]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[寵物]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[新聞]]></category>
